# Code of Conduct

## Our Pledge
We pledge to make participation in this project a harassment-free experience for everyone, regardless of age, body size, disability, ethnicity, gender identity and expression, level of experience, nationality, personal appearance, race, religion, or sexual identity and orientation.

## Our Standards
Examples of behavior that contributes to a positive environment include using welcoming and inclusive language, being respectful of differing viewpoints and experiences, and gracefully accepting constructive criticism.

Examples of unacceptable behavior include harassment, trolling, insulting or derogatory comments, and other conduct which could reasonably be considered inappropriate.

